This patch was last verified against llama.cpp tag b5000+.
llama.cpp moves fast — always apply against a recent tag.

Clone command (use latest tag or main):
    git clone https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp
    cd llama.cpp
    git checkout main   # or a specific tag e.g. b5200

Apply with:
    git apply ufm_custom_kernels.patch

If hunks drift (line numbers shift), apply manually.
Each hunk has a search anchor — grep for it in ggml-vulkan.cpp
and insert immediately after the anchor line.

Build requirements:
    - Vulkan SDK 1.4.341+ (https://vulkan.lunarg.com/sdk/home#windows)
    - CMake 3.21+
    - MSVC 2022 or GCC 12+  (no ROCm required on build machine)
    - Python 3.10+  (for header embedding step)

================================================================================

